00:42:24,360 --> 00:42:27,239
[SPEAKER_01] Iako su bili apsolutno izjednačeni makronutrijenti.

580
00:42:27,239 --> 00:42:30,800
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se tu kao glavni neki uzračnik pokazala ta,

581
00:42:30,800 --> 00:42:33,219
[SPEAKER_01] to se zove energetska gustoća.

582
00:42:33,219 --> 00:42:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko ubit ti energije dobiješ u volumenu hrane.

583
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] I ta ultraprocesirana hrana ima izrazito visokoenergetsku gustoću.

584
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:44,619
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, male porcije, ali izuzetno kalorične.

585
00:42:44,619 --> 00:42:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] I onda ti jednostavno puniješ svoj želudac

586
00:42:47,340 --> 00:42:50,400
[SPEAKER_01] i puno kasnije dobiješ taj dojam sitosti.

587
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:54,059
[SPEAKER_01] A unio si puno veću u količinu kilokalorija.

588
00:42:54,059 --> 00:42:58,059
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da nekako se čini da bi mogla baš ta energetska gustoća

589
00:42:58,059 --> 00:43:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] biti razlog zašto ultraprocesirana hrana

590
00:43:01,119 --> 00:43:05,139
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno toliko stvara problema u pitanju debljine.

591
00:43:05,139 --> 00:43:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je to krenulo, recimo naravno sa zapada,

592
00:43:07,619 --> 00:43:13,179
[SPEAKER_00] fast food, gazirana pića su nekako marketinjski

593
00:43:13,179 --> 00:43:15,179
[SPEAKER_00] predstavljena kao društveni faktor.

594
00:43:15,179 --> 00:43:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] Faktor socijalizacije.

595
00:43:16,539 --> 00:43:19,219
[SPEAKER_00] Znači sad ja i ti se družimo i naravno nećemo sad naručiti

596
00:43:19,219 --> 00:43:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] ili praviti geršlo, nego ćemo pojesti dva burgera

597
00:43:23,579 --> 00:43:25,739
[SPEAKER_00] na pizzu, nevam pojma, šta već.

598
00:43:26,619 --> 00:43:30,460
[SPEAKER_00] I sad se to, kao da je problem otišao da je to opostalo svakodnevnica,

599
00:43:30,460 --> 00:43:33,280
[SPEAKER_00] a ne nešto što je, ne znam, ja imam isto taj običaj.

600
00:43:33,280 --> 00:43:36,760
[SPEAKER_00] Lijepo mi je, gdje mi je lijepo da je ta neka hrana ukusna,

601
00:43:36,760 --> 00:43:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] a ne nužno zrava.

602
00:43:37,960 --> 00:43:42,519
[SPEAKER_00] Svedelce nekako opet cijela priča na umjerenost.

603
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] je li dovoljno napravdati kao umjereno je ok?

604
00:43:46,699 --> 00:43:48,300
[SPEAKER_01] Stoji li to?

605
00:43:48,300 --> 00:43:51,880
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, znaš šta je meni neka problem s tom kada kažu umjerenost je ok?

606
00:43:51,880 --> 00:43:53,980
[SPEAKER_01] Po čijim kriterijima umjereno?

607
00:43:53,980 --> 00:43:59,139
[SPEAKER_01] Nije isto moje umjereno i, neću reći tvoje, ne znam, tvoje navike.

608
00:43:59,139 --> 00:44:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] Reci imam višak, je li?

609
00:44:00,480 --> 00:44:01,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, ali ne znam ti navike.

610
00:44:01,679 --> 00:44:04,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ili recimo umjereno nekoga koji ima 20 kilograma viška.

611
00:44:04,639 --> 00:44:12,840
[SPEAKER_01] Naš, umjereno je, tipa, meni je umjereno da jedan put mjesečno pojede neki junk food, damo reći.

612
00:44:12,840 --> 00:44:15,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ne smijem sad govoriti, ovo je mena restorana gdje sjedava.

613
00:44:15,219 --> 00:44:16,460
[SPEAKER_01] Nemoj, nemoj, nemoj, nemoj.

614
00:44:16,460 --> 00:44:19,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, mislijem, znaš šta sam mislio, znaš šta sam mislio.

615
00:44:19,739 --> 00:44:20,440
[SPEAKER_01] Nemoj, nemoj.

616
00:44:20,440 --> 00:44:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ja ću govoriti.

617
00:44:21,199 --> 00:44:22,820
[SPEAKER_01] Nemo što si ih hvalio, nemoj reći.

618
00:44:22,820 --> 00:44:27,139
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, meni je to, recimo, umjereno.

619
00:44:29,139 --> 00:44:29,440
[SPEAKER_01] Jednom mjesečno.

620
00:44:29,440 --> 00:44:30,820
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo, to je meni umjereno.

621
00:44:30,820 --> 00:44:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek koji trenira, koji zna, ohrani puno više nego ostatak ljudi, jednom mjesečno.

622
00:44:37,119 --> 00:44:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, ajmo reći od prilike.

623
00:44:38,500 --> 00:44:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, sad sam imao neki period preko ljeta kada mi je opušteniji život,

624
00:44:41,539 --> 00:44:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] ali generalno u tom nekom kontekstu.

625
00:44:43,260 --> 00:44:45,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ilaj, ajmo reći, dva put mjesečno, razumiješ?

626
00:44:45,639 --> 00:44:48,820
[SPEAKER_01] Da ode na večer na pizzu, da ode na hamburger i tako.

627
00:44:48,820 --> 00:44:50,179
[SPEAKER_01] To je meni umjereno.

628
00:44:50,179 --> 00:44:52,159
[SPEAKER_01] A nekom bi to bilo ekstremno.

629
00:44:52,159 --> 00:44:55,659
[SPEAKER_01] Razumiješ? Zato mi je ta čita priča umjerenosti.

630
00:44:56,980 --> 00:45:00,199
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, ja sam mislim da će četiti da je umjereno sedam puta.

631
00:45:00,199 --> 00:45:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] Pa možda jest.

632
00:45:01,420 --> 00:45:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možda jest, razumiješ?

633
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:04,260
[SPEAKER_01] Teško mi je reći.

634
00:45:04,260 --> 00:45:05,719
[SPEAKER_01] Opet je bitan taj kontekst.

635
00:45:05,719 --> 00:45:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ti uz tih sedam puta dobro izgledaš,

636
00:45:09,380 --> 00:45:11,179
[SPEAKER_01] zadovoljan se energijom u razini dana,

637
00:45:11,179 --> 00:45:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] imaš dobre nalaze, nemaš nikakvih problema,

638
00:45:13,699 --> 00:45:15,500
[SPEAKER_01] to je za tebe umjereno.

639
00:45:15,500 --> 00:45:16,139
[SPEAKER_01] I to je okej.

640
00:45:16,139 --> 00:45:19,260
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, teško je naći...

641
00:45:19,260 --> 00:45:21,360
[SPEAKER_00] Teško mi je jasno definira šta znači umjereno.

642
00:45:21,360 --> 00:45:26,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kad bi usporedio neke prehramene navike u Hercegovini,

643
00:45:26,559 --> 00:45:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] poslije ne znam, je li se to mjeri uopće,

644
00:45:28,960 --> 00:45:30,079
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam kako se rada,

645
00:45:30,079 --> 00:45:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] li se neka izraživanja,

646
00:45:31,199 --> 00:45:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] u novije vrijeme, zadnje 20-ta godina,

647
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:37,440
[SPEAKER_00] možda od struka biti zadvojena prehramene navikama

648
00:45:37,440 --> 00:45:38,300
[SPEAKER_00] i možeš usporediti to.

649
00:45:38,300 --> 00:45:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, evo, budući da živiš dio života i Osijeku

650
00:45:41,420 --> 00:45:45,280
[SPEAKER_00] i Hercegovine i Slavonije su dosta i povijesno povezane.

651
00:45:45,280 --> 00:45:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš li to nekako usporediti

652
00:45:47,440 --> 00:45:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] i je li neko ko ocijenjuje

653
00:45:49,239 --> 00:45:50,340
[SPEAKER_00] i ko trebao to ocijenjivati,

654
00:45:50,340 --> 00:45:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] zadovoljen prehramene navikama?

655
00:45:52,539 --> 00:45:53,900
[SPEAKER_01] Pa našta ti je, znaš,

656
00:45:53,900 --> 00:45:56,980
[SPEAKER_01] no kako budu one karte po internetu,

657
00:45:56,980 --> 00:45:58,840
[SPEAKER_01] ono, za bilo koji parametar,

658
00:45:58,840 --> 00:46:00,179
[SPEAKER_01] pa ono, čitava Europa,

659
00:46:00,179 --> 00:46:01,460
[SPEAKER_01] pa sad ove zemlje zelene,

660
00:46:01,460 --> 00:46:03,119
[SPEAKER_01] ove crvene, ove narančaste,

661
00:46:03,119 --> 00:46:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] BiH si Iva uvijek.

662
00:46:04,559 --> 00:46:06,760
[SPEAKER_01] Nema podataka, ni za šta, znam.

663
00:46:06,760 --> 00:46:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sad je uzadnje vrijeme

664
00:46:07,960 --> 00:46:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] da naša agencija Sigurnost Hrane

665
00:46:09,539 --> 00:46:11,559
[SPEAKER_01] je počela rad puno, puno tih istraživanja,

666
00:46:11,559 --> 00:46:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] tako ćemo i možda griješim,

667
00:46:13,699 --> 00:46:15,179
[SPEAKER_01] možda smo već dobili podatke

668
00:46:15,179 --> 00:46:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] ili dobivamo podatke

669
00:46:16,380 --> 00:46:18,739
[SPEAKER_01] o nekim generalnim prehrambenim navikama

670
00:46:18,739 --> 00:46:20,219
[SPEAKER_01] populacije u BiH.

671
00:46:20,219 --> 00:46:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, prilično smo tankim na tom području,

672
00:46:23,000 --> 00:46:25,420
[SPEAKER_01] mogu ja ovako iz neke svoje obzervacije govoriti,

673
00:46:25,420 --> 00:46:27,119
[SPEAKER_01] ali sad baš jasno da se mogu pozvati

674
00:46:27,119 --> 00:46:29,320
[SPEAKER_01] na neke parametre, ne mogu.

675
00:46:29,320 --> 00:46:31,360
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, možda griješim,

676
00:46:31,360 --> 00:46:33,019
[SPEAKER_01] možda je to izašlo,

677
00:46:33,019 --> 00:46:35,440
[SPEAKER_01] ali donedavno nije bilo prisutno.

678
00:46:35,440 --> 00:46:38,019
[SPEAKER_01] U Hrvatskoj je malo drugačija opet situacija,

679
00:46:38,099 --> 00:46:40,519
[SPEAKER_01] opet oni imaju puno više tih nekih istraživanja

680
00:46:40,519 --> 00:46:42,760
[SPEAKER_01] i opet ima nekih konkretnih podataka

681
00:46:42,760 --> 00:46:44,139
[SPEAKER_01] koje ja sad ne mogu iz glave

682
00:46:44,139 --> 00:46:45,539
[SPEAKER_01] točno reći.

683
00:46:45,539 --> 00:46:47,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kažem, mogu ovako neku generalnu usporedbu

684
00:46:47,659 --> 00:46:49,579
[SPEAKER_01] napraviti, kao što si ti sam rekao,

685
00:46:49,579 --> 00:46:51,420
[SPEAKER_01] dosta sto povezane nekako.

686
00:46:51,420 --> 00:46:53,440
[SPEAKER_01] Zemlje je, ka bi morao, ne zemlje,

687
00:46:53,440 --> 00:46:55,440
[SPEAKER_01] kao bih rekao, regije.

688
00:46:55,440 --> 00:46:57,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ka bi morao naći neke dvije

689
00:46:57,280 --> 00:46:58,199
[SPEAKER_01] koje su najsličnije,

690
00:46:58,199 --> 00:47:00,300
[SPEAKER_01] možda bi te dvije mi bile nekako najsličnije

691
00:47:00,300 --> 00:47:01,639
[SPEAKER_01] po čisto nekim

692
00:47:01,639 --> 00:47:04,019
[SPEAKER_01] tradicijama hrane.

693
00:47:05,059 --> 00:47:06,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ali opet taj neki problem, jer

694
00:47:06,780 --> 00:47:08,840
[SPEAKER_01] nije isto selo i grad.

695
00:47:08,840 --> 00:47:11,019
[SPEAKER_01] U selu su neki totalno drugačiji običaji.

696
00:47:11,019 --> 00:47:12,920
[SPEAKER_01] Opet od u gradu, ti dominiraju pekare,

697
00:47:12,920 --> 00:47:15,059
[SPEAKER_01] dominiraju...

698
00:47:15,059 --> 00:47:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] neće niko do...

699
00:47:16,380 --> 00:47:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] Šta jedeš na malom odmoru, sir iz mijeha.

700
00:47:18,539 --> 00:47:19,920
[SPEAKER_01] Nije, razumije.

701
00:47:19,920 --> 00:47:21,519
[SPEAKER_01] Iako je to naša tradicija,

702
00:47:21,519 --> 00:47:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi odu pekari.

703
00:47:22,699 --> 00:47:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je teško naći neki,

704
00:47:23,960 --> 00:47:26,840
[SPEAKER_01] jel tako, opet konkretan odgovor na to.

705
00:47:26,840 --> 00:47:28,900
[SPEAKER_01] A kažem, opet i podaci bi trebali izaći,

706
00:47:28,900 --> 00:47:30,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa ćemo imati, ali mislim da generalno

707
00:47:30,400 --> 00:47:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne stojimo baš najbolje.

708
00:47:32,000 --> 00:47:34,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ranije smo se spominjali

709
00:47:34,460 --> 00:47:36,179
[SPEAKER_00] autofagije, keto prehrane

710
00:47:36,179 --> 00:47:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] i ostalih načina prehrane.

711
00:47:38,739 --> 00:47:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] Tu si isto u zadnje vrijeme

712
00:47:39,880 --> 00:47:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] javlja veliki problem,

713
00:47:41,420 --> 00:47:43,719
[SPEAKER_00] odnošno i predstavljam kao veliki problem.

714
00:47:43,719 --> 00:47:45,659
[SPEAKER_00] Vidim, dosta ljudi se bori s tim gluten.

715
00:47:45,659 --> 00:47:48,179
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se tu dogodilo?

716
00:47:48,179 --> 00:47:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] Aha.

717
00:47:48,800 --> 00:47:50,780
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to je isto zanimljiva priča.

718
00:47:50,780 --> 00:47:53,420
[SPEAKER_01] Gluten je protein iz žitarica.

719
00:47:53,420 --> 00:47:56,059
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, evo, zadovodim vaš tvojegu

720
00:47:56,059 --> 00:47:57,760
[SPEAKER_01] kopiju žitarice,

721
00:47:57,760 --> 00:47:59,059
[SPEAKER_01] ili pravu žitaricu, ne zna.

722
00:47:59,059 --> 00:48:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, svaka žitarica ima taj gluten.

723
00:48:02,119 --> 00:48:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] To je jednostavno protein koji se nalazi.

724
00:48:04,079 --> 00:48:05,559
[SPEAKER_01] E sad, određenite,

725
00:48:05,559 --> 00:48:07,699
[SPEAKER_01] kako mali broj ljudi

726
00:48:07,699 --> 00:48:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] ima celijakiju.

727
00:48:09,119 --> 00:48:11,539
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, nemogućnost probave toga glutena.

728
00:48:11,539 --> 00:48:12,440
[SPEAKER_01] Da mu to je najgori.

729
00:48:12,440 --> 00:48:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] I onda imaš te intolerancije na gluten.

730
00:48:15,480 --> 00:48:17,519
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je tu intoleranciju

731
00:48:17,519 --> 00:48:19,420
[SPEAKER_01] opet malo teže dokazati.

732
00:48:19,420 --> 00:48:21,940
[SPEAKER_01] I mislim da se opet nekakav prevelik naglasak

733
00:48:21,940 --> 00:48:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] stavlja na taj gluten

734
00:48:22,800 --> 00:48:26,019
[SPEAKER_01] kao neki glavni uzročnih problema,

735
00:48:26,019 --> 00:48:26,719
[SPEAKER_01] razumiješ.

736
00:48:26,719 --> 00:48:28,719
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno, ok, ako imaš celijakiju,

737
00:48:28,719 --> 00:48:30,760
[SPEAKER_01] da, jasno, očito smetati gluten,

738
00:48:30,760 --> 00:48:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] moraš izbaziti gluten.

739
00:48:31,840 --> 00:48:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ali već kad dolazim u to područje intolerancija,

740
00:48:34,420 --> 00:48:36,820
[SPEAKER_01] prilično je teško izolirati

741
00:48:36,820 --> 00:48:38,320
[SPEAKER_01] neki pojedinačni utjecaj.

742
00:48:38,320 --> 00:48:40,239
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, mislim da je malo previše opet stavljeno

743
00:48:40,239 --> 00:48:42,539
[SPEAKER_01] od tog nekog marketinga na gluten-free proizvode

744
00:48:42,539 --> 00:48:43,179
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

745
00:48:43,179 --> 00:48:45,380
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ono samo da piše na njemu gluten-free,

746
00:48:45,380 --> 00:48:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] to je u startu nešto dobro,

747
00:48:46,659 --> 00:48:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] je li tako?

748
00:48:47,119 --> 00:48:49,659
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno da je gluten u startu nešto loše.

749
00:48:50,320 --> 00:48:53,659
[SPEAKER_01] ali opet se možda možemo vratiti na ovu priču,

750
00:48:53,659 --> 00:48:54,780
[SPEAKER_01] te neke konstantnosti.

751
00:48:54,780 --> 00:48:56,659
[SPEAKER_01] jer ti, ako ti stvarno smeta gluten,

752
00:48:56,659 --> 00:48:59,340
[SPEAKER_01] ti u tjedan dana možete kontratiti smeta gluten.

753
00:48:59,340 --> 00:49:02,719
[SPEAKER_01] Kroz eliminaciju namjenica koje sadržuje gluten

754
00:49:02,719 --> 00:49:06,320
[SPEAKER_01] i praćenje svojeg odzivnog signala,

755
00:49:06,320 --> 00:49:08,659
[SPEAKER_01] odgovora kako se tijelo reagira,

756
00:49:08,659 --> 00:49:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] kako tijelo ponaša kada smo uklonili te namjenice.

757
00:49:10,800 --> 00:49:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da kažem, previše se naglaska stavlja na tako te neke sitne detalje.

758
00:49:16,500 --> 00:49:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možemo ne govoriti iz područja gdje jesmo.

759
00:49:19,079 --> 00:49:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tu smo kod nas i ja ne znam to,

760
00:49:22,019 --> 00:49:24,280
[SPEAKER_00] desetci generacija prije nas su odgojni,

761
00:49:24,280 --> 00:49:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] babe su šopalne, pitom, kruhom, peksimetima, uštipcima.

762
00:49:29,039 --> 00:49:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] Prije se jednostavno nije to znalo.

763
00:49:32,920 --> 00:49:34,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu ljudi imali smetnje?

764
00:49:34,199 --> 00:49:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je bila pšenca drugčija?

765
00:49:36,900 --> 00:49:41,000
